From the root project directory (besu) run:

`./gradlew ethereum:evmtool:jmhJar`

This should create .jar (`ethereum/evmtool/build/libs/evmtool-22.7.7-jmh.jar`). To run benchmark:

`java -jar ethereum/evmtool/build/libs/evmtool-22.7.7-jmh.jar -rf json -rff JSON_OUTPUT_FILE -bm ss -p code=CODE_TO_RUN`

it will produce some output to stdout/stderr and save results to JSON_OUTPUT_FILE in json format.
